sequenceDiagram
    actor Owner
    actor Guardian1
    actor Guardian2
    participant Contract as WayneLockGuardianRecovery 2-of-3
    participant Lit as Lit Protocol

    Note over Owner,Lit: Phase 1 Owner initiates recovery
    Owner->>Contract: startRecovery
    Contract->>Contract: recoveryActive = true recoveryId++ approvals = 0

    Note over Owner,Lit: Phase 2 Guardians approve within 5-min window
    Guardian1->>Contract: approveRecovery ownerAddress
    Contract->>Contract: approvals = 1 below threshold

    Guardian2->>Contract: approveRecovery ownerAddress
    Contract->>Contract: approvals = 2 meets threshold

    Note over Owner,Lit: Phase 3 Owner decrypts via Lit
    Owner->>Contract: isRecoveryApprovedForOwner
    Contract-->>Owner: true

    Owner->>Lit: litDecryptDek ciphertext hash ACC
    Lit->>Contract: isRecoveryApprovedForOwner owner
    Contract-->>Lit: true
    Lit-->>Owner: DEK bytes released

    Owner->>Owner: Decrypt all entries with DEK

    Note over Owner,Lit: Phase 4 Finalize
    Owner->>Contract: finalizeRecovery
    Contract->>Contract: recoveryActive = false approvals reset
